Ruuvi Station is an easy and fun way to use Ruuvi sensors at home and for your hobbies. The app is specifically designed to work with our open-source weatherproof RuuviTag Bluetooth sensors.

RuuviTag is an environmental sensor that continuously broadcasts sensor data over Bluetooth. This data can then be collected on any nearby device that has Ruuvi Station app installed. No Bluetooth pairing required.

RuuviTag devices have an excellent energy consumption profile with an average of 3 years battery life.

Ruuvi Station offers numerous possibilities to use RuuviTags, but that’s not all! Ruuvi devices are 100% open-source and can be used not only by private consumers, but also by businesses, developers, students and makers.
